Output artifacts/init-smoke.gif
Output artifacts/init-smoke.mp4

Set Shell bash
Set Width 1200
Set Height 760
Set FontSize 20
Set FontFamily "DejaVu Sans Mono"
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 18
Set Framerate 30
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.2
Set WaitTimeout 180s

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Type "iii --version"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "scripts/smoke-init.sh"
Enter
Sleep 15s
Sleep 2s
